hypre lobpcg中 HYPRE_lobpcg.c中对于tol有初始设置相对误差和绝对误差初始是1.0e-06

下面是lobpcg的收敛准则
175   notConverged = 0;
176   for ( i = 0; i < n; i++ ) {
177     if ( utilities_FortranMatrixValue( resNorms,  i + 1,  1 ) >
178          utilities_FortranMatrixValue( lambda,  i + 1,  1 )*rtol + atol
179          + DBL_EPSILON ) {
180       activeMask[i] = 1;
181       notConverged++; 
182     }
183     else 
184       activeMask[i] = 0;
185   }

